# childElements

**Instance Property**

An array that contains child text elements.

## Declaration

```swift
var childElements: [NSTextListElement] { get }
```

## Accessing the text elements

- **textList**: The value that represents the text list.
- **parent**: A text list element that refers to the enclosing text list element.
